```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant C as Client
  participant E as Edge (OpenResty)
  participant R as Redis
  participant S as Backend

  C->>E: GET /api/data (api_key)
  E->>E: Token bucket (per-IP) check
  alt IP bucket exceeded
    E-->>C: 429 + Retry-After
  else IP allowed
    E->>R: INCR api:{api_key}:{date} (quota)
    alt quota exceeded
      E-->>C: 429 + Retry-After + limit headers
    else quota ok
      E->>S: Proxy to backend
      S-->>E: 200 OK
      E-->>C: 200 OK + rate headers
    end
  end
```
